dct_title_s: Grundridsning af Fortet St. Louis paa Öen Sanaga eller Senegal
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
North oriented toward right of sheet.
Bar scale statement: Maalestav af 50 halve Favne eller Toises.
Index numbers but no apparent key.
Appears in Prévost's L'Histoire generale des voyages.
